data.description: Situated in a serene park-like setting, this exquisite property offers a harmonious blend of nature and luxury living. Conveniently set off the road, the residence boasts established trees, providing both shade and seclusion for the perfect retreat. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed split floor plan. Featuring two living quarters, this home is ideal for multigenerational living or as a space for guests or a home office. The heart of this home lies in its roomy master suite, a sanctuary of comfort featuring a luxurious jetted tub for relaxation. The large walk-in closet adds a touch of practicality, keeping your living spaces organized and clutter-free. The updated, bathroom with a larger entry door, adds a touch of inclusivity to the property, meeting the diverse needs of its occupants. With three bedrooms and three bathrooms in total, this home caters to both personal and guest needs with ease.This property is not only aesthetically pleasing but also incorporates smart features for a comfortable lifestyle. A Generac system ensures uninterrupted power, providing peace of mind during unexpected outages. The water filtration system and water softener contribute to a high standard of water quality throughout the home. Schedule a private tour and experience the beauty and functionality of this unique residence firsthand. Your dream home awaits!
